In standard SPI mode, this bit is always in default state.
",
"enum_values": "",
"lsb": "",
"mod_write_val": "",
"msb": "",
"read_action": "",
},
"MSB_Error": {"access": "read-write",
"bit_offset": "11",
"bit_range": "",
"bit_width": "1",
"desc": "MSB error.
This flag is asserted when:
  The core is configured in either dual or quad SPI mode and
