} Bits 0 Readable 1 ID Selected_Slave Writeable 1 Name Selected_Slave} {ParentID axi_quad_spi_0 Description {SPI Transmit FIFO Occupancy Register} Size 32 Readable 1 ID SPI_TXFIFO_OR Writeable 0 MemoryAddress 1105199220 Name SPI_TXFIFO_OR} {ParentID SPI_TXFIFO_OR Description {The binary value plus 1 yields the occupancy.
