  0 - Disabled.
  1 - Enabled.
} Bits {0 1 2 3} Readable 1 ID DTR_Underrun Writeable 1 Name DTR_Underrun} {ParentID IPIER Description {Data receive register/FIFO full.
  0 - Disabled.
  1 - Enabled.
} Bits {0 1 2 3 4} Readable 1 ID DRR_Full Writeable 1 Name DRR_Full} {ParentID IPIER Description {Receive FIFO overrun.
  0 - Disabled.
  1 - Enabled.
