} Bits {0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7} Readable 1 ID Slave_Select_Mode Writeable 1 Name Slave_Select_Mode} {ParentID IPIER Description {DRR_Not_Empty.   0 - Disabled.   1 - Enabled. Note: The setting of this bit is applicable only when FIFO Depth is set to 1 and the core is configured in slave mode of standard SPI mode.
